{"id":34685,"title":"Atypical focal cortical dysplasia in a patient with Cowden syndrome.","abstract":"A macrocephalic girl presented with generalised epilepsy due to focal cortical dysplasia. She later developed multiple hamartomatous lesions and was diagnosed to have Cowden syndrome. The diagnosis was confirmed by identification of a novel frameshift mutation in the PTEN gene of the patient. ","date":"2014-04-09","categories":"Congenital Hereditary and Neonatal Diseases and Abnormalities","split":"test","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24714173","annotations":[{"name":"Epilepsy","weight":0.863773,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Epilepsy"},{"name":"Gene","weight":0.847996,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gene"},{"name":"Mutation","weight":0.79024,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mutation"},{"name":"Lesion","weight":0.549525,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lesion"},{"name":"Macrocephaly","weight":0.474497,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Macrocephaly"},{"name":"Hamartoma","weight":0.371348,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hamartoma"},{"name":"Frameshift mutation","weight":0.360845,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frameshift_mutation"},{"name":"Cerebral cortex","weight":0.307319,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cerebral_cortex"},{"name":"Syndrome","weight":0.270177,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Syndrome"},{"name":"Dysplasia","weight":0.259972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dysplasia"},{"name":"Diagnosis","weight":0.180374,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diagnosis"},{"name":"Cortical dysplasia","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cortical_dysplasia"},{"name":"Cowden syndrome","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cowden_syndrome"},{"name":"PTEN (gene)","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wik